description:
This show is dedicated to all that wear skinny jeans. Tough job! Want to know how to get rid of unwanted house guests. Find out right here. Trump is making things tense and hatred is at an all time high. Who you mad at now? We ask The Steve Harvey Nation to call in and vent. Are You Smarter Than Tommy? Aniyah VS Tommy. Strawberry Letter involves something brand new. Fool #1 has a situation with the phone prank and so much more!
